<p style="margin:0 0 14px;">I have reached out a couple of times and want to make sure this landed in the right place. No pressure at all.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 14px;">The short version: One Algorithm LLC is a certified <strong>EDWOSB</strong> in AI, data engineering, and cloud modernization. We are actively building past performance and looking to partner with established firms on federal subcontracts where our certifications and technical skills create value.</p><p style="margin:0 0 14px;">As a certified EDWOSB, One Algorithm is also eligible for the SBA All Small Mentor-Prot&#233;g&#233; Program &#8212; if your organization has an interest in expanding set-aside access through a mentoring relationship, that may be worth a brief conversation as well.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 20px;">If there is an active RFP, a recompete, or anything in your pipeline — even a quick email pointing me to the right person would be hugely appreciated. Thank you for your time.</p>
